syllogism: All dogs are mammals. All mammals are animals. Therefore, all dogs are animals.
Some fish are creatures. All creatures are aquatic. Therefore, all fish are aquatic.
No trees are animals. All dogs are animals. Therefore, no dogs are trees.
Some stones are plants. All plants are growing. Therefore, all stones are growing.
No birds are reptiles. All snakes are reptiles. Therefore, no snakes are birds.
All cats are mammals. Some mammals are friendly. Therefore, all cats are friendly.
No water are solid. All ice are solid. Therefore, no ice are water.
All rocks are objects. Some objects are living. Therefore, all rocks are living.
No fish are mammals. All whales are mammals. Therefore, no whales are fish.
All dogs are animals. Some animals are pets. Therefore, all dogs are pets.
